{"word":"G4880 - συναποθνήσκω - synapothnḗskō - soon-ap-oth-nace'-ko - Be dead with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναποθνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synapothnḗskō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ap-oth-nace'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be dead with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடமரி,கூடச்சாகு"},{"paragraph":"to die together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G599 - ἀποθνήσκω - apothnḗskō - ap-oth-nace'-ko/599\">G599</a>; to <i>decease</i> (literally) in company <i>with</i>, or (figuratively) similarly <i>to:</i> - be dead (die) with.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G110/110\">G110</a>, <a href=\"#/G2288/2288\">G2288</a>, <a href=\"#/G2289/2289\">G2289</a>, <a href=\"#/G2348/2348\">G2348</a>, <a href=\"#/G2349/2349\">G2349</a>, <a href=\"#/G4776/4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800/4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806/4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832/4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833/4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854/4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855/4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862/4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880/4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891/4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916/4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957/4957\">G4957</a>, <a href=\"#/G599/599\">G599</a>"}]}